                              "Value": "NVIDIA Reflex Low Latency reduces PC latency and increases responsiveness by syncing up the CPU and GPU for more efficient rendering. In Boost mode, NVIDIA Reflex will save slightly more latency and attempt to optimize latency in CPU bound cases. Boost mode can slightly decrease FPS and increase GPU power draw."
