                              "PropertyTagExtensions": "NoExtension",
                              "Value": "- Fix door compressor   x\r\n- Gather resources:\r\n            Receivers   x\r\n            Electrodes   x\r\n            Thin wire   x\r\n            Rust scraps   x\r\n- Bait ant queen   x\r\n- O.R.C. Procedure   x\r\n- Improvement testing:\r\n            Infusion   x (some abilities)\r\n            Molars   x (mold is key)\r\n            Tumbling   x (missing something)\r\n            Laser attachments   x (very good)\r\n- Test run in the pumpkin patch   x\r\n- Find sabotage route for converted platoon   x\r\n- Workshop cleanup   x\r\n- Assign guards   x"
