                                  "Name": "StrProperty",
                                  "InnerCount": 0
                                }
                              ],
                              "PropertyTagExtensions": "NoExtension",
                              "Value": "I submit for immediate review a COUNTER proposal to my colleague’s ladybug idiocy.\r\n\r\nDo we have a sour spill problem in the garden? Maybe. Is the solution to this potential issue to strap office furniture to a bug? Are you insane?\r\n\r\nAccording to the domestication team, even simple ants are impossible to manage. We need a creature we can trust!\r\n\r\nLet’s use King Dozer, my pet lizard, to clear the sour spills. He is gentle, aloof, and can be easily motivated with treats. I brought him to the park today for a demonstration.\r\n\r\nThis will be MY final proposal for the cleanup efforts.\r\n\r\n– Employee 363"
                            },
                            {
                              "$type": "UAssetAPI.PropertyTypes.Objects.StrPropertyData, UAssetAPI",
                              "Name": "FemaleText",
                              "ArrayIndex": 0,
                              "PropertyGuid": null,
                              "IsZero": false,
                              "PropertyTagFlags": "None",
                              "PropertyTypeName": [
                                {
                                  "$type": "UAssetAPI.UnrealTypes.FPropertyTypeNameNode, UAssetAPI",
                                  "Name": "StrProperty",
